sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Client
    participant API as Post API
    participant OS as Object Store
    participant Proc as Image Processor
    participant CDN as CDN
    participant DB as Metadata Store
    participant FO as Fan-out Service

    Note over C,FO: UPLOAD PATH (pre-signed URL + async processing)
    C->>API: request upload (caption, location, tags)
    API->>OS: mint pre-signed PUT URL
    OS-->>API: pre-signed URL
    API-->>C: upload URL + post_id (pending)
    C->>OS: PUT raw image bytes (direct, bypassing API)
    OS-->>C: 200 stored
    OS-)Proc: object-created event

    Note over Proc,CDN: VARIANT GENERATION (async, off critical path)
    Proc->>Proc: hash check (CSAM / known-bad)
    alt fingerprint match
        Proc-XAPI: block + flag
    else clean
        par generate variants in parallel
            Proc->>OS: write thumbnail (100px)
        and
            Proc->>OS: write small (480px)
        and
            Proc->>OS: write medium (1080px)
        and
            Proc->>OS: write full (original, transcoded)
        end
        OS-->>Proc: variants stored
        Proc-)CDN: prewarm edges
    end

    Note over Proc,FO: PUBLISH (metadata + fan-out)
    Proc->>API: notify ready (variant URLs)
    API->>DB: persist post metadata + media_urls
    DB-->>API: ok
    API-)FO: hybrid push/pull fan-out to followers
    API-->>C: post visible (state = published)

    Note over C,CDN: READ PATH (feed picks resolution)
    C->>API: GET /feed?cursor
    API->>DB: load post metadata batch
    DB-->>API: posts + variant URL set
    API-->>C: feed payload (CDN URLs per resolution)
    C->>CDN: GET variant matching viewport + bandwidth
    CDN-->>C: image bytes
